Heather Mack is accused of killing her mother Sheila von Wiese-Mack in Bali last year . 
  The 19-year-old smiled and laughed as she took baby Stella to court in Denpasar today . 
  She and boyfriend Tommy Schaefer are accused of premeditated murder . 
  Prosecutors have asked judges to jail Mack for 15 years and Schaefer for 18 . 
  Mack maintains her innocence and says she is innocent of the murder . 
  Baby Stella was born in hospital last month and will stay with her mother . 
